            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, peel and roughly chop the <strong>garlic</strong> and peel (scrape the skin off with a teaspoon) and roughly chop (or grate) the <strong>ginger</strong></p><p>Slice the <strong>red chilli<span class=\"text-danger\">[es]</span></strong> finely and separate the <strong>coriander leaves</strong> from the stems</p><p>Bash the <strong>lemongrass</strong> with a <strong>rolling pin</strong>, then chop in half</p><p>Roll the <strong>lime<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span> </strong>with your hand on a hard surface (to release more juice) and cut in half</p>",
