            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once fragrant, add the <strong>coconut stock</strong> to the pot with the juice of 1/2 <span class=\"text-danger\">[1]</span> <strong>lime  </strong>and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to medium and cook, covered, for 10-12 min or until the butternut squash is fork-tender</p><p>Cut the <strong>remaining lime</strong> into wedges</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
