      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, dry, wide-based pan over a medium-high heat</p><p>Sprinkle the <strong>rotis </strong>with a little <strong>cold water</strong></p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>rotis</strong> to the pan and cook for 1-2 min on each side or until warmed through</p><p>Tip: Cooking for 4? You may need to do this in 2 batches!</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
