      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>Thai-style butternut squash soup</strong> in bowls with the <strong>warmed rotis</strong> to the side</p><p>Top the soup with the <strong>peanuts</strong>, <strong>remaining sliced chilli </strong>(not a fan of spice? Just add a little!)<strong> </strong>and <strong>remaining coriander leaves</strong></p><p>Garnish with a <strong>lime wedge</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
